    "summary": "I bring to the table a proactive, driven and results-oriented Business Development and Engineering Strategy Manager experienced in facilitating intergovernmental collaborations and national industry cluster strategies, and the bringing together of system development teams, multi-disciplinary cultural/trans-national teams and programs to execute complex projects from conception to final hand-over. \n\nArmed with a deep understanding of client needs to effectively respond with offerings designed to resolve issues and create sustainable income streams, I am highly respected for my listening skills translatable into technical requirements for engineers to create value. Additionally, I have the ability to network with teams to direct strategic new markets, technology, and globally competitive product development strategies. \n\nMy expertise encompasses the following:\n\u2022\tBusiness Development\n\u2022\tStrategic \u2013 Technology \u2013 Innovation Management\n\u2022\tKnowledge & Relationship Management\n\u2022\tTeam Optimization\n\u2022\tResearch & Development\n\u2022\tSystems & Enterprise Engineering\n\u2022\tFeasibility Studies\n\u2022\tStrategic Product & Market Positioning\n\u2022\tRoad Maps & Project Milestones\n\u2022\tBespoke & International Contracts\n\u2022\tRisk & Interface Management\n\u2022\tProcurement & Contracting Strategies\n\u2022\tExecution Planning\n\u2022\tProposal & Licensor Management\n\nCurrently working for the Council for Scientific and Industrial Research as an International Business Development Manager my biggest achievement has been the replication of a zero-international income in a competency area to achieve more than 80% in six years by employing strategy developments and opportunity facilitations towards large multi-year R&D contracts. \n\nMy education includes a Masters in (Executive) Business Administration and a Master of Engineering in Software Engineering. I have numerous awards and most recently completed Scrum Product Owner Certification.  Looking to emigrate to a new location\n\nPlease contact me should you require additional information. \n\n",
